  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/45b22977f4f459d5d8361427fddfa383.poster.avif?t=1765957969\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/45b22977f4f459d5d8361427fddfa383.webm?t=1765957969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/45b22977f4f459d5d8361427fddfa383.mp4?t=1765957969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive Until the End</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather survivors and escape from a world destroyed by zombies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEFENSURVIVOR</strong> is a strategy game where you construct obstacles and deploy survivors to fend off the zombies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize randomly assigned units to survive until the last moment! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>How to Play</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/8069574a7f758dd7169e44f2730b2c49.poster.avif?t=1765957969\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/8069574a7f758dd7169e44f2730b2c49.webm?t=1765957969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/8069574a7f758dd7169e44f2730b2c49.mp4?t=1765957969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Protect the shelter from the oncoming zombies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build walls around the shelter to limit the zombies' path.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deploy units to defeat the zombies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit new survivors with the currency earned from defeating zombies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You win by protecting the shelter for 15 minutes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine recruited units into higher-tier units to utilize stronger units.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Survivor Specialization</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/bbbbaa861e7c22cdffb2440962fab676.poster.avif?t=1765957969\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/bbbbaa861e7c22cdffb2440962fab676.webm?t=1765957969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/bbbbaa861e7c22cdffb2440962fab676.mp4?t=1765957969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Operate various classes with unique characteristics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select survivors and obtain stronger ones through the synthesis function.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find synergistic combinations of survivors.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat bosses to acquire the currency needed for synthesis.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ※<strong>Useful Tips</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can build and upgrade walls from the construction menu.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drag the survivor cards at the bottom to place them where desired.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click on deployed survivors to move, promote, or synthesize them.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click on supply crates dropped by the transport plane to obtain artifacts or additional survivors that aid in survival.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/45b22977f4f459d5d8361427fddfa383.poster.avif?t=1765957969\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/45b22977f4f459d5d8361427fddfa383.webm?t=1765957969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/45b22977f4f459d5d8361427fddfa383.mp4?t=1765957969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive Until the End</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather survivors and escape from a world destroyed by zombies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEFENSURVIVOR</strong> is a strategy game where you construct obstacles and deploy survivors to fend off the zombies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize randomly assigned units to survive until the last moment! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>How to Play</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/8069574a7f758dd7169e44f2730b2c49.poster.avif?t=1765957969\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/8069574a7f758dd7169e44f2730b2c49.webm?t=1765957969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/8069574a7f758dd7169e44f2730b2c49.mp4?t=1765957969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Protect the shelter from the oncoming zombies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build walls around the shelter to limit the zombies' path.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deploy units to defeat the zombies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit new survivors with the currency earned from defeating zombies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You win by protecting the shelter for 15 minutes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine recruited units into higher-tier units to utilize stronger units.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Survivor Specialization</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/bbbbaa861e7c22cdffb2440962fab676.poster.avif?t=1765957969\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/bbbbaa861e7c22cdffb2440962fab676.webm?t=1765957969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341760/extras/bbbbaa861e7c22cdffb2440962fab676.mp4?t=1765957969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Operate various classes with unique characteristics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select survivors and obtain stronger ones through the synthesis function.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find synergistic combinations of survivors.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat bosses to acquire the currency needed for synthesis.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ※<strong>Useful Tips</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can build and upgrade walls from the construction menu.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drag the survivor cards at the bottom to place them where desired.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click on deployed survivors to move, promote, or synthesize them.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click on supply crates dropped by the transport plane to obtain artifacts or additional survivors that aid in survival.</p></li></ul>",
